{"tid":834094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安局局長：香港民族黨今日就係一個非法社團","createTime":"2018-09-24T03:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T11:35:10.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":243,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"00da0c28753d874518d9f9a296e44196e5535695","tid":834094,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537753492_a6e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537753492_a6e5.jpg&h=c3126ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府刊憲，保安局局長李家超行使《社團條例》第8(2)條賦予保安局局長的權力，作出命令禁止香港民族黨在香港運作或繼續運作。命令在憲報刊登即日生效。香港民族黨召集人陳浩天回應查詢指，暫時不作回應。政府新聞處今早表示，李家超於上午11時會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n李家超表示，在申述期過後，收到有關人士申述，並在考慮有關方面的建議和申述後，決定基於維護國家安全、公共安全、公共秩序，禁止香港民族黨運作或繼續運作。換言之：「香港民族黨今日就係一個非法社團。」"},{"pid":"57e65be38a5919e76609401d81ec16a87be7aa25","tid":834094,"uid":35324,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b995fb7fde2fb8f97aad6bae60d953017f53c6","tid":834094,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"三合會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7310bff432c3b7c0915a022ec9a84a952e24ee72","tid":834094,"uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"痴線"},{"pid":"91d25abe453e7104b85efc716782c605fd5b8357","tid":834094,"uid":108467,"like":142,"dislike":5,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"通常一啲嘢愈打壓，發展得愈快。"},{"pid":"894ddd1adb5b98ffd31fe948ea9ffaffa06c29a3","tid":834094,"uid":36178,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"無晒言論自由囉, 支持97回歸嘅正冚家剷"},{"pid":"4c2b0af66c82b57889c55841ea76c7ba4aef0d49","tid":834094,"uid":189,"like":147,"dislike":2,"