ke":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ab9cf1a6d65802d1693804a760d68bd4c6e99aa","tid":834094,"uid":92467,"like":90,"dislike":3,"score":87,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"14k<br />\n新義安<br />\n和勝和<br />\n民族黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"黑澀會"},{"pid":"3e24ca04245e5dcccfda9e7c532d89d6a0b6003f","tid":834094,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"照計中聯辦, 人大 都係非法組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db67cf61bbf47b876accf76418c7c914f1550b5","tid":834094,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"跟住整個&quot;真香港民族黨&quot;係咪又可以無限loop ??"},{"pid":"657e6f06ed9ab311fd0bb20cac64a4f91bce98ff","tid":834094,"uid":124804,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"強烈建議成立香港共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf3be30e71b6d2677a7829316ff115f49b932a3","tid":834094,"uid":136216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除非英國肯出手<br />\n求其取消某個高官嘅屋企人英籍</blockquote>英國佬唔會咁做啦<br />\n<br />\n敘利亞獨裁者巴沙爾個老婆都有英國籍<br />\n<br />\n巴沙爾做咁多衰野, 英國都冇對佢老婆個身份同權利做過乜o野啦</blockquote>英國佬太君子&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; <br />\nbtw不過我諗班高官依家都好驚<br />\n佢哋舊年上任,未必估到事情發展得咁快<br />\n喺中共眼中其實呢班人只係用完即棄嘅condom<br />\n唯有瘋狂表忠希望爆大獲嗰陣自己唔會上身<br />\n咁嘅局勢,佢哋萬一要走佬返外國都一定比人搞</blockquote><br />\n但是，現在美國已對鄰國解放軍後勤將令凍結美國資產，這班香港condom做這些動作，將來都有幾會發生相同情況！"},{"pid":"c7197a30eb19712b9ab1b6e8b5bdb820aacdf944","tid":834094,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"點解入民族黨？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊馬。<br />\n我唔妥你，我可以𢭃你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以𢱕你。<br />\n𡃁仔你睥咩呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？<br />\n你見過冧友未呀？你見過死人未呀？<br />\n你話陳浩天你偶像吖嘛，你見過陳浩天未呀？<br />\n銅鑼灣揸fit人吖嘛，好巴閉呀？<br />\n你知唔知佢大佬畀人冧咗佢掹唔到；<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢條女，死，佢救唔到。<br />\n你知唔知陳浩天諗緊咩呀？<br />\n話畀你聽佢唔想做揸fit人，<br />\n佢唔想入民族黨，<br />\n但係佢冇辦法，冇得返轉頭。<br />\n係呀，每個人都有偶像，我都有。<br />\n其實，讀唔讀書，我理唔到咁多，<br />\n但係我想話畀你聽，行啱路，唔洗返轉頭。"},{"pid":"78f7248e978d089440268f456956755fa10412ca","tid":834094,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a663e8ccd6f1007ca5f49714f4c9e4b6c5cc36e6","tid":834094,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"連兒登仔打飛機既言論自由都無埋<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩贏新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767479e2c50b2a9679a37dbb3195c1396234462b","tid":834094,"uid":38030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"打擊黑社會唔見你有咁快，保安局?改名叫保共局算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ad06f82ee3177dc699173f1967b3dfc141fd5b","tid":834094,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cdedcedce2af62335d29f4dd1cf04cb97de10c2","tid":834094,"uid":1009,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"另一邊廂 「自決派」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n提都唔敢提，直接變平凡的幸福就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/131348_7fbcaf0489398202ccca26f6449c6703.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F131348_7fbcaf0489398202ccca26f6449c6703.png&h=8b0e756a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60b6abe112a87c73d148e43c0093854